  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduo a KWave</title>

    <para>
      The <application>KWave</application> package contains a KF5 based Sound
Editor application.
    </para>

    &lfs113_checked;

    <bridgehead renderas="sect3">Informao do Pacote</bridgehead>
